---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="New Client Special Offers | Elegant Lashes Orange County"
  description="Exclusive first-time client specials on lash extensions in Orange County. Save on your first full set at our Irvine, Tustin, Santa Ana, and Costa Mesa locations!"
  keywords="lash extension deals, first time lash specials, Orange County lash discounts, new client offers OC"
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-20 bg-lightbg">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to Blog
      </a>

      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="text-sm text-primary font-medium mb-4">August 12, 2025</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-playfair text-darktext mb-6">New Client Special Offers</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mediumtext">Discover exclusive first-time client specials on premium lash extensions at our Orange County locations!</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Ready to experience the beauty and convenience of lash extensions? Elegant Lashes by Katie welcomes new clients with exclusive special offers designed to help you discover why thousands of Orange County residents trust us with their lashes. Whether you're curious about classic lashes or ready to try dramatic volume, we have the perfect introductory package for you!</p>

        <h2>Current New Client Specials</h2>

        <h3>First-Time Classic Lash Special</h3>
        <p>Perfect for lash extension beginners!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full classic lash set application</li>
          <li>Complimentary consultation and lash mapping</li>
          <li>Professional aftercare kit included</li>
          <li>15% off your first fill appointment</li>
          <li><strong>Special new client pricing (save up to $50!)</strong></li>
          <li>Available at all four Orange County locations</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Volume Lash Discovery Package</h3>
        <p>Experience the drama of volume lashes!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full volume lash set (2D-3D)</li>
          <li>Extended consultation to design your perfect look</li>
          <li>Premium lash care products</li>
          <li>Complimentary lash refresh within first week</li>
          <li><strong>New client exclusive pricing (save up to $75!)</strong></li>
          <li>Upgrade to 4D-6D volume at special rate</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Hybrid Lash Starter Package</h3>
        <p>Best of both worlds - natural texture with added volume!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom hybrid lash set</li>
          <li>Personalized style consultation</li>
          <li>Deluxe aftercare kit with cleanser and spoolie</li>
          <li>Photo session to capture your new look</li>
          <li><strong>First-time client rate (save $60!)</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why New Clients Love Our Specials</h2>

        <h3>No Risk Trial</h3>
        <p>Our new client specials make it affordable to try lash extensions without a huge commitment. Experience the convenience and beauty at a special introductory price!</p>

        <h3>Complete Experience</h3>
        <p>Every package includes everything you need:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Thorough consultation with certified lash artist</li>
          <li>Professional application in comfortable studio</li>
          <li>Aftercare products and instructions</li>
          <li>Follow-up support and guidance</li>
          <li>Special pricing on future appointments</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Expert Guidance</h3>
        <p>As a new client, you'll receive extra attention and education:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detailed explanation of the process</li>
          <li>Help choosing the perfect style</li>
          <li>Comprehensive aftercare training</li>
          <li>Tips for maximizing retention</li>
          <li>Answers to all your questions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Additional New Client Benefits</h2>

        <h3>Complimentary Add-Ons</h3>
        <p>First-time clients receive these extras at no additional charge:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Lash mapping to design your perfect look</li>
          <li>Before and after photos</li>
          <li>Travel-size lash cleanser</li>
          <li>Professional spoolie brush</li>
          <li>Aftercare instruction card</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Loyalty Program Enrollment</h3>
        <p>New clients automatically join our rewards program:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Earn points with every service</li>
          <li>Birthday month special offers</li>
          <li>Exclusive member-only promotions</li>
          <li>Referral rewards program</li>
          <li>Priority booking during busy seasons</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Flexible Scheduling</h3>
        <p>We make it easy for new clients to find the perfect appointment time:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Same-week appointments often available</li>
          <li>Evening appointments for working professionals</li>
          <li>Weekend availability</li>
          <li>Four convenient Orange County locations to choose from</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to Claim Your New Client Special</h2>

        <h3>Step 1: Choose Your Location</h3>
        <p>Select from our four Orange County studios:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Irvine:</strong> Central OC location with ample parking</li>
          <li><strong>Tustin:</strong> Convenient for North OC residents</li>
          <li><strong>Santa Ana:</strong> Easy freeway access</li>
          <li><strong>Costa Mesa:</strong> Perfect for beach communities</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 2: Book Your Appointment</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Call or text: 657-334-9919</li>
          <li>Book online through our website</li>
          <li>Mention "New Client Special" when booking</li>
          <li>Choose your preferred lash style package</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 3: Prepare for Your Appointment</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Arrive with clean lashes (no mascara or makeup)</li>
          <li>Bring inspiration photos if desired</li>
          <li>Plan for 1.5-2 hours of relaxation</li>
          <li>Come ready to ask questions!</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 4: Enjoy Your New Lashes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Receive full aftercare instructions</li>
          <li>Schedule your first fill appointment</li>
          <li>Start earning loyalty rewards</li>
          <li>Share your gorgeous new look!</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Seasonal Promotions</h2>

        <h3>Summer Lash Special (June-August)</h3>
        <p>Beach-ready lashes for Orange County summer!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Extra discount for waterproof lash styles</li>
          <li>Free summer care tips consultation</li>
          <li>Bonus travel-size products</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Back to School Special (August-September)</h3>
        <p>Students save extra with valid student ID:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Additional 10% off new client packages</li>
          <li>Flexible scheduling around class schedules</li>
          <li>Student loyalty discounts on fills</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Holiday Glam Special (November-December)</h3>
        <p>Look stunning for all your holiday events!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Volume upgrade at no extra charge</li>
          <li>Complimentary lash refresh before New Year's</li>
          <li>Holiday party-ready styles</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Bring a Friend Promotion</h2>
        <p>New clients who book with a friend receive additional perks:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Both receive 10% extra discount</li>
          <li>Coordinated appointment times</li>
          <li>Shared private studio experience</li>
          <li>Both earn double loyalty points</li>
          <li>Champagne or refreshments during service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What Makes Our New Client Experience Special</h2>

        <h3>Certified Lash Artists</h3>
        <p>All our Orange County lash technicians are:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Professionally certified and licensed</li>
          <li>Experienced with thousands of clients</li>
          <li>Trained in latest techniques</li>
          <li>Passionate about lash artistry</li>
          <li>Committed to client satisfaction</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Premium Products</h3>
        <p>We use only the highest quality materials:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Professional-grade lash extensions</li>
          <li>Medical-grade adhesives</li>
          <li>Hypoallergenic options available</li>
          <li>Cruelty-free and ethically sourced</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Comfortable Environment</h3>
        <p>Our Orange County studios feature:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Clean, spa-like atmosphere</li>
          <li>Comfortable lash beds</li>
          <li>Soothing music and ambiance</li>
          <li>Professional lighting</li>
          <li>Refreshments available</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <h3>Can I use multiple specials at once?</h3>
        <p>New client specials cannot be combined with other offers, but you'll automatically receive the best available discount.</p>

        <h3>Do new client specials expire?</h3>
        <p>Promotions are subject to change. Book within 30 days of your first inquiry to guarantee current pricing.</p>

        <h3>What if I'm not happy with my lashes?</h3>
        <p>We offer complimentary adjustments within 48 hours. Your satisfaction is guaranteed!</p>

        <h3>Can I refer friends after using my new client special?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely! You'll earn referral rewards for every friend you send our way.</p>

        <h3>Are fills included in the new client special?</h3>
        <p>The special covers your first full set. Fill appointments are discounted for new clients (typically 15% off).</p>

        <h2>Real New Client Reviews</h2>

        <h3>Michelle T. - Irvine</h3>
        <p>"The new client special made trying lash extensions so affordable! The consultation was thorough, and my lashes turned out exactly how I wanted. I'm hooked and already booked my fill!"</p>

        <h3>Sophia R. - Costa Mesa</h3>
        <p>"I was nervous about trying lash extensions, but the special pricing made it easy to take the leap. My lash artist was so patient with all my questions. The whole experience was amazing!"</p>

        <h3>Lauren K. - Santa Ana</h3>
        <p>"Best decision ever! The new client package included everything I needed. Two weeks later, my lashes still look perfect. Worth every penny, and the special made it even better!"</p>

        <h2>Don't Wait - Book Your New Client Special Today!</h2>
        <p>These exclusive offers won't last forever! Join thousands of satisfied Orange County clients who have discovered the beauty and convenience of professional lash extensions. Book your new client appointment today at Elegant Lashes by Katie and experience the difference that certified expertise and premium products make.</p>

        <p><strong>Limited Time Offer:</strong> Book your new client appointment this month and receive a complimentary lash serum sample ($25 value) with your service!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-sunset p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-playfair text-darktext mb-4">Claim Your New Client Special!</h3>
        <p class="text-darktext mb-6">Book now in Irvine, Tustin, Santa Ana, or Costa Mesa and save on gorgeous lashes!</p>
        <button type="button" class="open-modal-button main-book-now-btn text-xl">
          <span>Book New Client Special</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

